Class CharacterObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mmue_lm3.gameobjects.GameObject
      • com.example.mmue_lm3.gameobjects.CharacterObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Drawable, Updatable, java.lang.Comparable<GameObject>
    public class CharacterObject
extends GameObject
    Character GameObject which is there for creating, drawing, updating an detecting collision. Also many functionalities for the Gameplay are implemented here.
